title: NFL ATL: Week 15 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 15 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra -- recap all of the Week 15 action including the nail-biter between the Green Bay Packers and the Dallas Cowboys. Don’t miss the key takeaways and analysis from each game, then help the heroes by nominating them for the 2013 Stitcher Awards at stitcher.promotw.com. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
